{"tid":2095112,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"甄子丹《热血无赖》电影即将开拍！游戏改编主打动作","createTime":"2020-07-05T08:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:39:36.000Z","uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf7e0ed83ffbb3d74f22883d77487e03773f502","tid":2095112,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"今天甄子丹在微博发视频动态表示：&ldquo;开始为下一个挑战作准备了！&rdquo;，能看到正文一旁带上了&ldquo;新电影&rdquo;&ldquo;sleepingdog#&rdquo;和&ldquo;热血无赖&rdquo;这几个标签。看来由他主演的《热血无赖》游戏改编电影即将正式开拍了。<br />\n<br />\n从几年前开始《热血无赖》就传出筹备真人电影的消息，在2018年初甄子丹则正式确认自己将主演本片。当时甄子丹还表示，游戏里的主角沈威在武打动作风格上会自己非常相似，这个角色简直感觉就是为自己量身定制的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/upimg/pic/2020/07/05/small_202007051457189209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fupimg%2Fpic%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2Fsmall_202007051457189209.jpg&h=d963fe7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前《热血无赖》电影尚未公布上映日期和具体故事梗概，不过随着之后电影的正式开拍，相信很快就会有更多消息披露。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/upimg/pic/2020/07/05/origin_202007051455518627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fupimg%2Fpic%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2Forigin_202007051455518627.jpg&h=199b2420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家識做啦，既然套戲關於香港，香港人最有話事權，Twitter 文宣 Ready <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20200626/zhen_zi_dan_nan_wang_2017nian_xiang_gang_hui_gui_20zhou_nian_._1_Medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Finline_images%2F20200626%2Fzhen_zi_dan_nan_wang_2017nian_xiang_gang_hui_gui_20zhou_nian_._1_Medium.jpg&h=06c09bb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24b89bd8d085cf8fd8896b5c97fdbb576c1862e5","tid":2095112,"uid":46151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"等我話你知咩叫眼